      <t>   This document describes OSPFv2 and OSPFv3 extensions for distributing
   the BitPositions configured on a Bit-Forwarding Router (BFR) with
   MPLS and non-MPLS encapsulation for "Bit Index Explicit Replication
   Traffic Engineering" (BIER-TE) in a BIER-TE domain.


